---
title: Carb Smart Brie and Apple Salad with Honey-Blueberry Dressing
description: All your favourite salad toppings in one meal! Creamy brie, crunchy, walnuts, sweet apples and savoury croutons! A drizzle and toss of the honey blueberry vinaigrette will send this salad over the edge!

